.Dd November 20, 2023
.Dt MAT_GETHEADER 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm Mat_GetHeader
.Nd Returns the header of a MATLAB MAT file given a MAT file structure.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Fd #include <matio.h>
.Ft const char *
.Fo Mat_GetHeader
.Fa "const mat_t *matfp"
.Fc
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn Mat_GetHeader
function returns the header of the MATLAB MAT file given by the MAT file
structure.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr Mat_CreateVer 3 ,
.Xr Mat_Open 3 ,
.Xr Mat_GetFileAccessMode 3 ,
.Xr Mat_GetFilename 3 ,
.Xr Mat_GetVersion 3
